{
  "stem": "7094.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's difficult, but I would say that perhaps 40% of the population was Jewish in the little town, 40% Ukrainian, and 20% Poles, because it was part of the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and we lived only with Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We only mixed with Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't have any contact with-- except in class, in school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But, we-- we-- the whole center of the town, the market with the building around the market, was mostly Jewish shops and Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had about three synagogues in this little shtetl.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a very Jewish background.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, very orthodox.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hasidic.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He belonged to the [NON-ENGLISH] rabbi, and he was a real believer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was-- he was afraid-- I missed the word.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What I wanted to say is assimilation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was against it, and he thought that education would bring assimilation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And also because we didn't have secondary education, it meant going to Lwow to gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the family in Lwow was already more-- less religious, so he was afraid of this influence.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had '38, a very sad year, because I wanted to go to further education, which he objected to it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I know now that he meant it, because he was really a very, very true, even-- he was tested.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, very often during the war, I could see he would rather not eat, however hungry he was, if it wasn't kosher.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If he went to work, he would come back on the Sabbath and dress in black and study the Tanakh.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Also, it was forbidden he would communicate with other people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we had contact over the roofs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was really a very true, religious man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a very religious-- I never questioned it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was that.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
